description.en:
Sasuke Inu is an Ethereum Mainnet token that allows the market to determine its value. It is designed for quick trade and uses the Proof-of-Stake consensus method. With Sasuke Inu tokens, you can do DeFi and yield farming. The fees for the Sasuke Inu coin on the Ethereum Mainnet are extremely cheap. The Sasuke Inu Token is a deflationary cryptocurrency, a 12% tax is applied to each transaction made.

We're creating an ecosystem of Sasuke Inu NFTs. Selected artists and designers from the community of Sasuke Inu will be invited to release the first Sasuke Inu Branded NFTs and NFT Game Cards.

Sasuke Inu strives to contribute to helping those in need, be it people, nature, or animals. The Charity campaigns are to be conducted through a partnership with leading brands and charitable organizations as well as via auctions of unique NFTs created especially for that reason.
